articles.author: Anders Hagstrom
articles.title: US launches missile-detecting satellites into orbit as concerns about Russia in space grow - Fox News
articles.description: The U.S. launched missile-detecting satellites into orbit on Thursday, just hours after news of a potential Russian threat to America's military satellites.
